### Module Registry Service API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5100

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Get All Modules
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules

### 3. Get Active Modules
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/active

### 4. Get Modules with UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/ui

### 5. Get Modules with Mobile Support
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/mobile

### 6. Get Specific Module (HR)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/hr

### 7. Register HR Module Manually (with Mobile Support)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleId": "hr",
  "displayName": "Human Resources",
  "description": "Manage employees, departments, onboarding, and benefits",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "apiBaseUrl": "http://localhost:5001",
  "uiEntryPoint": "http://localhost:5002/hr",
  "icon": "mdi-account-group",
  "permissions": [
    "hr.read",
    "hr.write",
    "hr.admin"
  ],
  "capabilities": [
    "employees",
    "departments",
    "onboarding",
    "benefits"
  ],
  "healthUrl": "http://localhost:5001/health",
  "tenantMode": "tenant-per-database",
  "supportsMobile": true,
  "mobileUISpecUrl": "http://localhost:5001/api/hr/mobile/ui-spec",
  "mobileContractVersion": "1.0.0"
}

### 8. Register Accounting Module (Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleId": "accounting",
  "displayName": "Accounting",
  "description": "Financial management, invoicing, and reporting",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "apiBaseUrl": "http://localhost:5003",
  "uiEntryPoint": "http://localhost:5002/accounting",
  "icon": "mdi-calculator",
  "permissions": [
    "accounting.read",
    "accounting.write",
    "accounting.admin"
  ],
  "capabilities": [
    "invoices",
    "expenses",
    "reports"
  ],
  "healthUrl": "http://localhost:5003/health",
  "tenantMode": "tenant-per-database"
}

### 8. Register Inventory Module (Example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleId": "inventory",
  "displayName": "Inventory",
  "description": "Stock management and warehouse operations",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "apiBaseUrl": "http://localhost:5004",
  "uiEntryPoint": "http://localhost:5002/inventory",
  "icon": "mdi-package-variant",
  "permissions": [
    "inventory.read",
    "inventory.write",
    "inventory.admin"
  ],
  "capabilities": [
    "stock-levels",
    "warehouses",
    "transfers"
  ],
  "healthUrl": "http://localhost:5004/health",
  "tenantMode": "tenant-per-database"
}
